--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 --                              Epochs                                      --
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Epochs is a simple 'mobile' all-client-side application that converts dates
from one time format to another.

Several formats are supported:
 - Gregorian
 - Julian
 - Modified Julian
 - Julian Calendar
 - Hebrew
 - Islamic
 - Persian
 - Indian Civil

The app doesn't require any server side processing, as it does it all with
javascript in the user's browser. Thus: super simple to put up on a website!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The pages are built with:
 - jquery
 - jqtouch
 - jspec
 - John Walker's calendar.js and astro.js calendar libraries! 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you wanna see an example of the app running you can check it out here:

http://epochs.pinedesk.biz
